    "description": "Your portal to the endless experiences in virtual world, owned by you.<br>Deverse World is a sandbox game with diversified gameplays and contents. We provide a playground and tools for users and players to play and contribute to the never-ending journey.<br>Deverse World is made by players, for players.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Free style gameplay</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/0801ee74d06283b091a22cbeb807fe87.poster.avif?t=1732716704\" width=476 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/0801ee74d06283b091a22cbeb807fe87.webm?t=1732716704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/0801ee74d06283b091a22cbeb807fe87.mp4?t=1732716704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Turn into any character races, from superhuman to wukong and even wizard in a free-style combat environment, there is no limitation in gameplays.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be Anything</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/4574754488afb61b602eded3b3ee387a.poster.avif?t=1732716704\" width=480 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/4574754488afb61b602eded3b3ee387a.webm?t=1732716704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/4574754488afb61b602eded3b3ee387a.mp4?t=1732716704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Be anyone you like to be, either your own virtual avatar, a knight in medieval, a soldier in modern time, or turn into a monster and any non-human beings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be Anywhere</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/30b9d60b946bfc89b4c103c92167c38c.poster.avif?t=1732716704\" width=476 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/30b9d60b946bfc89b4c103c92167c38c.webm?t=1732716704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/30b9d60b946bfc89b4c103c92167c38c.mp4?t=1732716704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Travel across different worlds, hosted and created by the users, experience different sceneries and environments.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create Anything</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/ed8bfe37721d179caf7433b73a9aa205.poster.avif?t=1732716704\" width=476 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/ed8bfe37721d179caf7433b73a9aa205.webm?t=1732716704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/ed8bfe37721d179caf7433b73a9aa205.mp4?t=1732716704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/81ea1e7f2740ee644f5d3064e245435f.poster.avif?t=1732716704\" width=480 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/81ea1e7f2740ee644f5d3064e245435f.webm?t=1732716704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242830/extras/81ea1e7f2740ee644f5d3064e245435f.mp4?t=1732716704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Immerse yourself into the journey of transforming your vision into gameplay with our <strong>Deverse World Editor</strong> and <strong>Unreal Engine SDK</strong>. You can create anything, from immersive stories, to a virtual concert of your favorite, to even a brand new shooter game with our custom FPS template. Share them with your friends and communities with ease!",
